configuration.value: for(var i = 0; i < records.length; i++) {  try {    if (!records[i].value['fileType']) {      state['dataFilePath'] = records[i].value['objectKey'];    } else {      state['infoFilePath'] = records[i].value['objectKey'];    }    if (state['dataFilePath'] && state['infoFilePath']) {      newRec = sdcFunctions.createRecord('Data and Control event record');      newMap = sdcFunctions.createMap(true);      newMap['dataFilePath'] = state['dataFilePath'];      newMap['infoFilePath'] = state['infoFilePath'];      newRec.value = newMap;      output.write(newRec);    }      } catch (e) {    // Send record to error    error.write(records[i], e);  }}
